595
00:26:12,960 --> 00:26:13,790
Lai.

596
00:26:13,810 --> 00:26:14,600
I'm sorry.

597
00:26:14,630 --> 00:26:15,420
I...

598
00:26:15,470 --> 00:26:17,040
