742
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:52,550
This herb is...

743
00:32:53,130 --> 00:32:54,290
Water hemlock!

744
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:56,070
So,

745
00:32:56,390 --> 00:32:57,670
Lai's death wasn't caused by

746
00:32:57,940 --> 00:32:58,910
firefly mushrooms.

747
00:32:58,940 --> 00:33:00,250
